<title>Preface</title>

<para>
    The goal of this document, a project of 
    <link xlink:href="http://www.olpcsf.org/"> olpcSF.org</link>,
    is to provide helpful documentation of the pathagar book
    server project and more specifically to help with installation,
    configuration and usage of this service software on low energy
    requiring hardware.  We began with the DreamPlug but have since
    switched to the Raspberry Pi as our device of choice.
</para>

